In [[True Way|Yuuzhan Vong religion]], the '''Twin Gods''' were [[Yun-Yammka]], the God of War, and [[Yun-Harla]], the Goddess of Deception. Together, they promoted victory in battle over the enemies over the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], and were held in great reverence by the Yuuzhan Vong. Only [[Yun-Yuuzhan]] surpassed them in official importance, though many privately held the Twin Gods in greater regard. They had a holiday known as the [[Festival of the Twin Gods]].

During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], the [[Solo twins]] came to be associated with the Twin Gods ([[Darth Caedus|Jacen]] due to his defeating of [[Warmaster]] [[Tsavong Lah]], [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina]] because she had declared herself an avatar of Yun-Harla). Twin Gods was also used to refer to [[Yun-Txiin]] and [[Yun-Q'aah]], the [[Lover Gods]].

